This was my 9th trip to Rome and I could not have been at a better location, just steps from my favorite place, The Piazza Navona.	The location is near our favorite and best piazza in Rome and most of the popular sites are within walking distance.	The biggest selling point is location - Piazza Navona is perfect with traders and many pizzerias, Vatican is 15 mins walk as are the Spanish steps.	It was conveniently located near Piazza Navona, which is within walking distance of all the major sites in Rome.